<li id="cite_note-abc.net.au-36"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-abc.net.au_36-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-abc.net.au_36-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text">Kerry O'Brien December 10, 2003 7:30 Report, <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.abc.net.au/7.30/content/2003/s1007523.htm">abc.net.au</a></span></li>
